                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980912-63-off369 t17980912-63-cd370"></join>, sixteen yards of linen cloth, value 20s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17980912-63-victim651" type="victimName">
