                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980912-63-defend649 t17980912-63-punish374"></join>
               Confined three months in Newgate
            </rs>, and <rs id="t17980912-63-punish375" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980912-63-punish375" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17980912-63-punish375" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980912-63-defend649 t17980912-63-punish375"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. COMMON SERJEANT.</p>
